Text:
Thanks for the higher quality. 
I could definitely hear the garbage with Jim's show, and the compression was bad too. Can't wait for the next one.
Don't know why I like the "Best of R&F" so much.  Always find something ya missed in the 1st run through.  Damn that Ronnie B.  Thanks again MG.

Well, they've got the whole week off so it's Best of's throughout, enjoy. Also, coming up around June 15th through the 21st I will be away and unable to up. I will still try to grab everything and up it when I get back though. Sometimes the goose has to fly, arf arf.
